#: ../../source/getting_started/overview.rst:2
msgid "Overview"
msgstr "概述"

#: ../../source/getting_started/overview.rst:3
msgid ""
"MaxFrame is a framework for large-scale data computation built on "
"MaxCompute by Alibaba Cloud with API-compatibility for pandas. It intends"
" to become an inplace replacement for Python users familiar with Numpy or"
" Pandas APIs to utilize MaxCompute to run their code in a distributed "
"environment."
msgstr ""
"MaxFrame 是一个基于阿里云 MaxCompute 构建的大规模数据计算框架，与 pandas "
"API 兼容。它旨在成为熟悉 Numpy 或 Pandas API 的 Python 用户的原位替代方案"
"，使他们能够利用 MaxCompute 在分布式环境中运行代码。"

